      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Honest Deal \u2013 Project Car or Budget Ride! \ud83d\udd27 Looking for an affordable set of wheels or a hands-on project? This car is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it shows significant wear both inside and out, including body imperfections, interior wear, and mechanical issues that will need attention. It's not a showroom star, but at this price point it offers real value for a budget-conscious buyer, a DIY mechanic, or someone needing basic transportation while they sort out repairs. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, just an honest deal!",
